   This page describes the SeqAn repository structure, including the [[Infrastructure/RepositoryStructure#Sandboxes| structure of sandboxes]]
*[[Infrastructure/BuildSystem| The CMake-Based Build System]]
   This page describes the CMake-based build system of SeqAn and the CMake modules shipped with SeqAn.
